  23 Dec 2008; Sebastian Pipping <sebastian@pipping.org>
  colormake-0.2.ebuild, Manifest :
  Bring back double quotes for SRC_URI as well

  23 Dec 2008; Sebastian Pipping <sebastian@pipping.org>
  colormake-0.2.ebuild, Manifest :
  Bring back double quotes as requested

  23 Dec 2008; Sebastian Pipping <sebastian@pipping.org>
  colormake-0.2.ebuild, Manifest :
  Remove superfluous EAPI=0, no longer restrict mirror,
  reduce quoting, replace doexe by dobin, reduce keywords to
  ~x86, delete Makefile so make is not called.
  Thanks to tommy and scarabeus.

  23 Dec 2008; Sebastian Pipping <sebastian@pipping.org>
  colormake-0.2.ebuild, Manifest :
  Mask all keywords, remove empty src_compile

  22 Dec 2008; Sebastian Pipping <sebastian@pipping.org>
  colormake-0.2.ebuild, Manifest :
  Remove superfluous entries to RESTRICT, fix quoting, thanks to
  Elias Pipping

  22 Dec 2008; Sebastian Pipping <sebastian@pipping.org>
  colormake-0.2.ebuild, colormake-0.2-disable-broken-tagging.patch,
  Manifest :
  Turn off mirror usage, patch out broken error tagging, cosmetics
